race.comment: ATMOSPHERE (1) has a solid record over this distance range with three wins and eight placings from 15 attempts and will be able to sit up on speed jumping from the favourable draw. Nicely placed to play a pivotal role. CASROCK (10) has been plying her trade in harder races in town and should find this task more to her liking. Will be hitting the line with gusto. KODIAK (6) is a bit of a hit or miss type but is more than capable enough on his day. Top-three candidate on best figures. SUPER QUICK (9) saves his best form for this distance range and gets Wiggins back on board. In the mix. GIVING DELIGHT (3) rounds out the selections.
